{"tid":1326174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"721基督徒請進","createTime":"2019-07-17T06:25:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-17T06:26:41.000Z","uid":251414,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c412d1483ea6ad1d4dd0049d95a8dc1db215b77a","tid":1326174,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:25:01.000Z","msg":"......<br />\n因為兒子藐視父親， 女兒抵擋母親， 媳婦抗拒婆婆， 人的仇敵就是自己家裏的人。  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">至於我，我要仰望耶和華， 等候那救我的上帝；</span></span> <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我的上帝必應允我。</span></span>  我的仇敵啊，不要向我誇耀。 我雖跌倒，仍要起來； 雖坐在黑暗裏，耶和華卻作我的光。  我要承受耶和華的惱怒， 直到他為我辯護，為我伸冤， 因我得罪了他； 他要領我進入光明， 我必得見他的公義。  那時我的仇敵看見這事就羞愧， 他曾對我說：「耶和華－你的上帝在哪裏？」 我必親眼見他遭報， 現在，他必被踐踏，如同街上的泥土。<br />\r\n彌迦書 7:6‭-‬10 RCUV"},{"pid":"e51f943265fd32fed8f2f67471dc9daeb2391e69","tid":1326174,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:25:43.000Z","msg":"我無野推"},{"pid":"a8e9c5dbf4fa9017471683baa1b45fb8165c3448","tid":1326174,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:26:01.000Z","msg":"我無野推"},{"pid":"d1a54b5bb4c997a1a84536de22dfa147c2b3efaf","tid":1326174,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:26:11.000Z","msg":"我無野推"},{"pid":"be477f1f0cd173eed1a77b7acffcbf8990503d04","tid":1326174,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:26:21.000Z","msg":"我無野推"},{"pid":"53a72e2e6525e8a3fcf53f6d40b7f0f108e2f063","tid":1326174,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:26:31.000Z","msg":"我無野推"},{"pid":"6500bd8cdff54691aa5899be5bd2e515a5074607","tid":1326174,"uid":251414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-17T06:26:41.000Z","msg":"我無野推"}]}